  "body": "> When scrolling through lots of messages, there is a very noticeable \"stutter\", and I'm concerned that this is due to the images being downloaded and possibly the logic of LinksMessage (which access appSettings). We may need to find a way to offload the downloading of images to a new thread, or only download images once scrolling has stopped for a period (like 100ms).\r\n\r\nPlease see the \"Notes\" section of the PR description https://github.com/status-im/nim-status-client/pull/1528#issue-539079152 for more information.",
